{"questionId":"3378296","questionHtml":"<p>Find the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>recognition of setting&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>r</mi></mrow></mfrac></math> to zero&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>attempt to substitute <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>7</mn></math> in for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>r</mi></math> in their derivative&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>04</mn><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>14</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>08</mn></mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi></mfrac><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>p</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi><mo>×</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>7</mn></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>(</mo><mi>p</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>)</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>(</mo><mo>$</mo><mo>)</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>35</mn></math> (per square metre) <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>(</mo><mo>(</mo><mo>$</mo><mo>)</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>34621</mn><mo>…</mo><mo>)</mo></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Accept <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>$</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>34</mn></math>, as this will also lead to a radius of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>